" -----------------
" Quickstart Guide:
" -----------------
" Start `ipython qtconsole`, `ipython console`, or  `ipython notebook` and
" open a notebook using you web browser.  Source this file, which provides new
" IPython command
"
"   :source ipy.vim
"   :IPython
